#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/ma/extras.py:docstring
#: of numpy.ma.extras.apply_along_axis:48
msgid ""
"The output array. The shape of `out` is identical to the shape of `arr`, "
"except along the `axis` dimension. This axis is removed, and replaced with "
"new dimensions equal to the shape of the return value of `func1d`. So if "
"`func1d` returns a scalar `out` will have one fewer dimensions than `arr`."
msgstr ""

